Website features
=======
* Mobile support
* Different presenter/student views
    - Student view tracks presenter view
    - Password protected presenter view
* Uploading and sharing results

Slides
=======
* Clustering slide
    - Illustrate images being different (have them pop up and compare them)
    - Illustrate images being similar (have them pop up and compare them)
* Noise slide
    - Noise definition
        - Why it is called noise
            - Compare to the term "background noise"
            - Something that is random, hard to interpret
* Diffusion model slide
    - Random noise initializations lead to different random outputs
        - A limitation of diffusion models -- why you see different random outputs when asking for the same thing
        - A way to identify generated outputs
        - But also a cool feature

